== 逸闻 ==
山本寬在Fractale播出之前接受報刊採訪時表示，如果本部動畫不成功便隱退。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://acg.178.com/201011/84243636363.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101229230948/http://acg.178.com/201011/84243636363.html |archive-date=2010-12-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>不久，山本寬關閉其博客並收回隱退宣言。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://acg.178.com/201101/89941934558.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120330041518/http://acg.178.com/201101/89941934558.html |archive-date=2012-03-30 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>結果該片收視冷淡，故事原案[[東浩紀|東浩紀]]表示山本寬應對此負責。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://acg.178.com/201104/96682362943.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111230224416/http://acg.178.com/201104/96682362943.html |archive-date=2011-12-30 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>而由于山本宽收回隐退宣言的行为，导致之后他所监督的作品在中国有了“遗作”之称 <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/micro-reading/dzh/2014-01-02/content_10945784.html |title=山本宽评价自己新动画制作很用心 |access-date=2019-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304211216/http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/micro-reading/dzh/2014-01-02/content_10945784.html |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。而该作品第一卷销量883卷也被爱好者将作品和其名字定为销量单位量（单位名称取作品名称缩写为“frt”，读作“宽”），用于和其他作品销量的对比来调侃。<ref>{{cite web |title=《电波教师》动画销量引发诸多吐槽 |url=http://cartoon.southcn.com/c/2015-09/04/content_132146762.htm |accessdate=2015-10-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150920005114/http://cartoon.southcn.com/c/2015-09/04/content_132146762.htm |archivedate=2015-09-20 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

